** Vim

 - C-R C-W : insert the word under the cursor.
 - :bufdo - do something in all buffers.
 - :GrepBuffer
 - C-v : to insert special characters.
 - :%!xxd and %!xxd -r : to convert the buffer into/back from hex mode

